Subject: [PATCH] Convert to Vite React app and add GitHub Pages deployment

- Scaffold Vite 5 + React 18 project (package.json, vite.config.js, index.html)
- Add src/main.jsx entry point and src/App.jsx (full app component)
- Configure base path /messaging-queue-learning/ for GitHub Pages subpath
